The paper discusses a method for debugging answer set programming (ASP) which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves logical reasoning and constraint solving which are topics covered in the sub-categories of logic in computer science (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the coding process and debugging which are topics covered in the sub-category of software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper involves querying and finding solutions which are topics covered in the sub-category of databases (cs.DB).
